---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="SoulWrap™ — JZ Stafura"
  description="Existential Wellness Solution. Patented Ontological Compression Technology. One Size Embraces All."
>
  <div class="back"><a href="/fun/">&#x2190; Fun</a></div>

  <section class="hero">
    <p class="overline">Fun / Parody</p>
    <h1>SoulWrap™</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Existential Wellness Solution. Because the abyss gazes also, but at least it's cozy.</p>
    <div class="tags">
      <span>Parody</span>
      <span>Wellness Culture</span>
      <span>Continental Philosophy</span>
      <span>Deadpan</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="preview-section">
    <a href="https://jzstafura.github.io/soulwrap/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="preview-card">
      <div class="preview-inner">
        <p class="preview-headline">You Can't Outrun Your Existential Dread</p>
        <p class="preview-sub">But you can wrap it.</p>
        <div class="preview-features">
          <div class="pf">
            <span class="pf-stat">87%</span>
            <span class="pf-label">reduction in midnight existential spirals</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pf">
            <span class="pf-stat">&#x221e;</span>
            <span class="pf-label">improved capacity to commit to ultimately futile projects</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pf">
            <span class="pf-stat">&#x2713;</span>
            <span class="pf-label">works if life is inherently absurd</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="preview-cta">
        Experience SoulWrap™ &#x2197;
      </div>
    </a>
    <p class="preview-note">A parody product landing page. The "Order Now" button links to the Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy entry on Existentialism.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="about">
    <h2>About This Project</h2>
    <p>SoulWrap™ is a deadpan parody of luxury wellness branding — the kind that promises ontological transformation through proprietary fabric technology and carefully selected lifestyle photography. It takes the form of a full product landing page, complete with comparison tables, testimonials, and a genuinely absurd ingredient list.</p>
    <p>The target is the genre of wellness marketing that appropriates the language of depth (mindfulness, authenticity, presence) while selling something that can be shipped in two days. SoulWrap™ takes that logic to its natural conclusion: what if the product just directly addressed the void?</p>
    <p>Built in vanilla HTML/CSS/JS. No framework needed for absurdism.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .back { padding: 1.5rem 0 0; }
  .back a { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-muted); text-decoration: none; }
  .back a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }

  .overline { font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .hero { padding: 2.5rem 0 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .hero-sub { max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }

  .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .tags span { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-muted); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; }

  .preview-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }

  .preview-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
  }

  .preview-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .preview-inner { padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem; }

  .preview-headline {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: normal;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .preview-sub {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .preview-features { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(180px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }

  .pf {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .pf-stat { font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text); font-family: var(--font-mono); }
  .pf-label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.4; }

  .preview-cta {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: var(--color-text);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .preview-note { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-muted); margin-top: 0.75rem; font-style: italic; }

  section.about { padding-bottom: 2rem; }
  .about h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .about p { color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1rem; max-width: 65ch; }
</style>
